{
  "stem": "27347.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were towns like Tarnow and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they don't-- I did not speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the towns did not mean that much to me because only the events, only peace, only my family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw either the cruelties or kindnesses of people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We started, again, walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We walked to a town where we were let in to sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was someone my grandparents knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were supposed to leave to Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At night, a man came to steal something and shot their daughter dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was a Polish man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Again, tragedy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The next day, again, into-- through the woods and kept on going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at one time-- we used to hide when we saw someone on the road before or after us-- but this was a truck.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We couldn't escape.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And those were about five, six men in their 30s-- 20s and 30s.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I found out later that they were Ukrainian men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They jumped off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They stopped the truck, jumped off, and started talking to my grandfather, my father, all the men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then they said, you're out of luck because we're going to kill you all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] were numb.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But there was no screaming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was no-- only huddling, my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my grandfather said, let them go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Take me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my father said, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Let them go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Take me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Let my father go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Let them go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I'll give you anything you want.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He says, whatever I have is yours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Let us-- let them go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He said, I'll tell you what, whoever misses the bullet will be lucky.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They lined us up.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
